<pre><code>$("#dialog-confirm").dialog({     resizable: false,     modal: true,     title: "dialogBox",     height: 550,     width: 700,      buttons: {       "Ok": function () {             $(this).dialog('close');             callback(true);         },             "Cancel": function () {             $(this).dialog('close');             callback(false);         }     }    }); </code></pre>  <p>I am using jquery-ui.css and dtree.css but when dialog box appears the scrollbar shows in left edge in chrome and mozilla but in IE9 the horizontal scrollbar always shows little open in right side  so i have to always scroll left to open the tree structure.</p>